descriptionHtml:
This is a two story house located just off of the road, southwest of Riverwood. You will find the location of the home marked by a shack icon on your map. Inside you will find abundant storage, an enchanting table, an alchemy lab, a bed, and a cooking pot. Riverwood is just a short stroll away for occasions when you must visit a merchant or address blacksmithing needs.

Version 1.1
- Rotated the map marker 180 degrees in order to place the player facing the home after fast traveling to the cabin.

Version 1.2
- Finalized the navmesh for the interior and exterior. I\'d forgotten that step in earlier versions.
author: Phong
